Union of Kenya Civil Servants national treasurer Justus Mugo yesterday claimed Manyatta MP John Muchiri tried to shoot him in Gakwegori village at 9am. Mugo said Muchiri&rsquo;s convoy blocked the way and the MP came out brandishing a pistol. But Muchiri said he was on his way to Embu town when Mugo blocked the way and insulted him. He denied brandishing a pistol.